detaileddescription.para: Debug option to have bubbles on all player controllers in a stand alone game. This is especially useful for testing and profiling these systems. This will also disable the ClientsViewers functionality. If UE_ALLOW_DEBUG_REPLICATION_BUBBLES_STANDALONE is set UE_REPLICATION_COMPILE_SERVER_CODE will be defined as 1 so server only code is compiled in standalone builds.
